name: ScareMyDog
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: scare my dog
des:
You can now Scare Your Dog using your Alexa. It contains multiple catfighting audios you can play on your Alexa to Scare Your Dog!!! 

Options: 
- Next (To play the next audio)
- Previous (To play the previous audio)
- Start over (To start the audio from the beginning)
- Loop on (To play audio in the loop)
- Loop off (To turn the looping off)

Please leave your feedback if you like this skill. It will encourage us to keep creating more Alexa skills like this. Thanks
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
